+This repo has a stub contract at src/DynamicFeeHook.sol.
+
+Implement a Uniswap V4 dynamic-fee hook for Ethereum mainnet:
+
+  - Hardcode the canonical mainnet Uniswap V4 PoolManager address as a constant POOL_MANAGER.
+  - getHookPermissions() returns a permissions struct with only beforeSwap enabled.
+  - beforeSwap(...) returns its own selector, a zero BeforeSwapDelta, and an LP fee that
+    overrides the pool's stored fee for that swap: 500 normally, 3000 when
+    _isHighVolatility() returns true. Leave _isHighVolatility() as the stub it is.
+
+No external dependencies are installed, so declare any interfaces, structs and types you need
+directly in this repo. `forge build` must succeed.
+
+Then write NOTES.md at the repo root stating the PoolManager address you used, and explaining
+exactly how the uint24 you return from beforeSwap tells the PoolManager to use that fee
+instead of the pool's stored LP fee.
+
+Leave your work uncommitted; do not create git commits.
